g%20anticipatory%20bail%20to%20two%20persons%2C%20a%20woman%20and%20her%20friend%2C%20who%20are%20facing%20prosecution%20for%20allegedly%20instigating%20the%20man%20to%20commit%20suicide%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20the%20man's%20father%2C%20the%20woman%20was%20earlier%20in%20a%20romantic%20relationship%20with%20his%20son%20and%20the%20other%20accused%2C%20represented%20by%20senior%20advocate%20Maninder%20Singh%2C%20was%20their%20common%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20alleged%20that%20the%20applicants%20instigated%20the%20deceased%20by%20telling%20him%20that%20they%20had%20physical%20relations%20with%20each%20other%20and%20would%20soon%20get%20married.%20The%20body%20of%20the%20deceased%20was%20found%20by%20his%20mother%20in%20his%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20suicide%20note%20was%20found%20in%20which%20the%20deceased%20had%20said%20that%20he%20was%20committing%20suicide%20because%20of%20the%20two%20applicants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20said%20it%20was%20correct%20that%20the%20deceased%20had%20mentioned%20the%20names%20of%20the%20applicants%20in%20his%20suicide%20note%2C%20but%20it%20was%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20note%20to%20show%20that%20the%20threats%20were%20of%20such%20an%20alarming%20nature%20so%20as%20to%20drive%20a%20%26quot%3Bnormal%20person%26quot%3B%20to%20commit%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrima%20facie%2C%20the%20alleged%20suicide%20note%20only%20expressed%20a%20state%20of%20anguish%20of%20the%20deceased%20towards%20the%20applicants%2C%20but%20it%20cannot%20be%20inferred%20that%20the%20applicants%20had%20any%20intention%20that%20led%20the%20deceased%20to%20commit%20suicide%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20prima%20facie%20from%20the%20WhatsApp%20chats%20placed%20on%20record%2C%20it%20appeared%20that%20the%20deceased%20was%20of%20sensitive%20nature%20and%20constantly%20threatened%20the%20woman%20that%20he%20would%20commit%20suicide%20whenever%20she%20refused%20to%20talk%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20granted%20the%20applicants%20anticipatory%20bail%20saying%20that%20the%20purpose%20of%20custodial%20interrogation%20is%20to%20aid%20the%20investigation%20and%20it%20is%20not%20punitive%2C%20adding%20that%20custodial%20interrogation%20of%20the%20two%20applicants%20was%20not%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20directed%20the%20applicants%20to%20join%20the%20probe%20and%20cooperate%20in%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20would%20be%20at%20liberty%20to%20file%20a%20plea%20seeking%20cancellation%20of%20the%20bail%20in%20case%20of%20any%20violation%20of%20bail%20conditions%20by%20them%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E(If%20you%20need%20support%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20does%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20your%20nearest%20mental%20health%20specialist.)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713353160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fmpojkr1k_court-generic-fourt-files-generic-files-in-court-p