turn%20of%20122%20is%20a%2035%20per%20cent%20jump.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20from%20the%20poll%20of%20opinion%20polls%20is%20drawn%20from%20nine%20polls%2C%20including%20three%20conducted%20by%20ABP-C%20Voter%20on%20December%2025%2C%20March%2012%2C%20and%20April%2016.%20In%20these%20three%2C%20the%20NDA's%20expected%20score%20jumps%20from%20295-335%20to%20366%20and%20settles%20at%20373%2C%20while%20INDIA%20goes%20from%20163%20down%20to%20156%20and%20then%20155.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20predicted%20returns%20for%20the%20BJP-led%20alliance%20comes%20from%20Times-ETG%2C%20which%20gives%20it%20between%20358%20and%20398%20seats%2C%20and%20gives%20INDIA%20110-130.%20The%20non-aligned%20parties%20are%20given%2064-68%20seats%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20TV-CNX%2C%20Zee%20News-Matrize%2C%20and%20Times-Matrize%20all%20give%20the%20NDA%20over%20350%20seats%20each%2C%20and%20give%20INDIA%20less%20than%20100%20seats.%20The%20exception%20is%20Times%20Matrize%2C%20which%20gives%20the%20bloc%20104%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20closest%20prediction%20is%20India%20Today-C%20Voter%3B%20a%20sample%20of%20nearly%2036%2C000%20voters%20polled%20on%20February%208%20indicates%20a%20return%20of%20335%20for%20the%20NDA%2C%20166%20for%20the%20INDIA%2C%20and%2042%20for%20other%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDA%20Clean%20Sweep%20In%208%20States%2C%20UTs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20is%20predicted%20to%20ride%20to%20victory%20on%20the%20back%20of%20clean%20sweeps%20in%20eight%20states%20and%20union%20territories%2C%20including%20national%20capital%20%3Cstrong%3EDelhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Mr%20Modi's%20home%20state%20of%20%3Cstrong%3EGujarat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cstrong%3EArunachal%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20flexed%20its%20nationalist%20muscles%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Chinese%20aggression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20is%20also%20tipped%20to%20sweep%20%3Cstrong%3ERajasthan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20building%20on%20last%20year's%20Assembly%20election%20win%20-%20Chandigarh%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EUttarakhand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EHimachal%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Dadra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli%2C%20and%20Daman%20and%20Diu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fml7osvd8_lok-sabha-election-2024_625x300_17_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20these%20states%20and%20UTs%20send%2072%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Winning%20these%2C%20if%20that%20is%20what%20happens%2C%20will%20give%20the%20BJP%20a%20significant%20edge%20in%20the%20final%20tally%2C%20particularly%20since%20the%20opinion%20polls%20suggest%2C%20as%20is%20widely%20expected%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20will%20once%20again%20fail%20to%20impress%20in%20South%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20election%20the%20BJP%20swept%20Delhi%20(seven%20seats)%2C%20Gujarat%20(26)%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20(two)%2C%20Chandigarh%20(one)%2C%20Uttarakhand%20(five)%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20(four)%2C%20and%20Daman%20and%20Diu%20(one).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20also%20claimed%2024%20of%20Rajasthan's%2025%20seats%3B%20the%2025th%20went%20to%20an%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20To%20Dominate%20Hindi%20Heartland%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20expected%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20allies%20will%20likely%20thump%20rivals%20in%20%3Cstrong%3EUttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Bihar%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Of%20the%20149%20seats%20in%20play%20here%2C%20the%20NDA%20could%20win%20a%20massive%20137.%20That%20return%2C%20if%20true%2C%20will%20almost%20match%20its%202019%20score%3B%20it%20won%2039%20of%20Bihar's%2040%20seats%2C%2074%20of%20UP's%2080%20and%2028%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Cstrong