ssing%20the%20daily%20average%20by%20over%203%20times.%20India%20vs%20Australia's%20World%20Cup%20match%20on%20November%2019%20showed%20cab%20payments%20dropping%20by%2028%25%20between%202%20and%2010%20pm%2C%20as%20millions%20tuned%20in%20to%20watch%20the%20game%20at%20their%20homes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713348240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Fijvqmeuo_india-generic_625x300_28_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-india-spent-its-money-in-2023-report-reveals-financial-habits-5461096%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20report%20analysed%20over%20a%20billion%20transactions%20conducted%20on%20its%20platform%20between%20April%201%2C%202023%2C%20and%20March%2031%2C%202024%2C%20revealing%20the%20areas%20where%20Indian%20consumers%20spent%20their%20money.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-india-spent-its-money-in-2023-report-reveals-financial-habits-5461096%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-india-spent-its-money-in-2023-report-reveals-financial-habits-5461096%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-india-spent-its-money-in-2023-report-reveals-financial-habits-5461096%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Battle%20Royale%20Rajasthan%3A%205%20Factors%20Shaping%20BJP's%20Hat-Trick%20Bid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F91era2o_pmmodi_640x480_22_November_23.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20temperature%20has%20begun%20to%20soar%20in%20the%20desert%20state%20with%20voting%20for