%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fex-bjp-rajasthan-ally-hanuman-beniwal-to-fight-lok-sabha-polls-from-nagaur-5307298%5C%22%3EHanuman%20Beniwal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Jat%20leader%20from%20the%20Rashtriya%20Loktantrik%20Party%20who%20won%20from%20Nagaur%20in%202019%20under%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20has%20now%20aligned%20with%20the%20Congress.%20Jats%20are%20an%20influential%20community%2C%20accounting%20for%20around%2012%25%20of%20the%20population.%20In%202019%2C%2085%25%20of%20Jats%20voted%20for%20the%20NDA%2C%20up%20from%2038%25%20in%202014%2C%20due%20to%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20RLP%20and%20the%20popularity%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20However%2C%20this%20support%20was%20reduced%20to%2042%25%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections.%20Jats%20and%20Rajputs%20share%20a%20traditional%20rivalry%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Congress%20hopes%20that%20the%20farmers'%20unrest%20and%20alliance%20with%20Beniwal%20could%20pull%20Jats%20towards%20the%20party%2C%20potentially%20denting%20the%20BJP's%20votes.%20Jats%20wield%20significant%20influence%20in%20the%20Shekhawati%20and%20Marwar%20regions%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Rajput%20Trouble%20Brewing%20For%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20controversial%20remark%20by%20Union%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspecial.ndtv.com%2Fndtv18kavote-136%2Fnews-detail%2Fparsottam-rupala-is-in-trouble-for-giving-controversial-statement-on-kshatriyas-is-bjp-preparing-to-change-the-candidate-from-rajkot-5389176%2F2%5C%22%3EParshottam%20Rupala%20in%20Gujarat%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20sparked%20protests%20that%20have%20spread%20to%20several%20states.%20Over%2060%25%20of%20the%20upper%20castes%20(including%20Brahmins%20and%20Rajputs)%20backed%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20last%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20the%20state.%20Although%20Rupala%20has%20withdrawn%20his%20remarks%20and%20publicly%20apologised%20to%20the%20community%2C%20the%20anger%20persists.%20Rajputs%20in%20Rajasthan%20demand%20that%20the%20BJP%20pull%20him%20from%20the%20fray%20in%20Rajkot.%20Rajput%20community%20organisations%20have%20linked%20the%20statement%20to%20denigrating%20their%20valour%20and%20sacrifices%20for%20the%20country.%20Parallelly%2C%20independent%20candidate%20Ravindra%20Singh%20Bhati's%20rise%20in%20Barmer%20is%20being%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Brevolt%20of%20the%20Rajputs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Alliance%20Problems%20For%20Congress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20fielded%20candidates%20in%2022%20seats%20and%20has%20an%20understanding%20with%20its%20INDIA%20bloc%20ally%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20(CPI-M)%20in%20Sikar%2C%20the%20RLP%20in%20Nagaur%2C%20and%20the%20newly-formed%20Bharatiya%20Adivasi%20Party%20(BAP)%20in%20the%20tribal-dominated%20Banswara%20constituency.%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20account%20for%2013%25%20of%20Rajasthan's%20population.%20Though%20traditionally%20supporters%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20BJP%20gained%20a%20lead%20in%20the%20community%20in%202019%2C%20with%2058%25%20backing%20the%20saffron%20party.%20However%2C%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20polls%2C%2051%25%20backed%20the%20Congress%20and%20only%2029%25%20supported%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20facing%20rebellion%20in%20Banswara.%20It%20reached%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20BAP%20very%20late%20and%20allotted%20the%20party%20symbol%20to%20Arvind%20Damor.%20However%2C%20although%20a%20deal%20has%20been%20sealed%2C%20the%20official%20Congress%20candidate%20has%20not%20withdrawn%20his%20nomination%20despite%20a%20directive%20from%20the%20state%20Congress%20committee.%20The%20party%20has%20not%20taken%20action%20against%20him%20yet%20and%20hopes%20to%20reach%20some%20sort%20of%20an%20understanding.%20However%2C%20this%20has%20created%20confusion%2C%20which%20could%20split%20the%20ST%20vote%2C%20ultimately%20aiding%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Internal%20Discontent%20Within%20The%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20dropped%2010%20sitting%20MPs%2C%20causing%20unrest.%20Leaders%20like%20Rahul%20Kaswan%20and%20Prahlad%20Gunjal%2C%20who%20rebelled%20against%20the%20party's%20decision%20to%20deny%20them%20tickets%20from%20Churu%20and%20Kota%2C%20respectively%2C%20have%20joined%20the%20Congress.%20Kaswan%20has%20received%20a%20ticket%20from%20Churu%2C%20and%20Gunjal%20is%20challenging%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20in%20Kota.%20Kaswan%2C%20a%20Jat%20leader%20with%20a%20formidable%20presence%20among%20members%20of%20Rajasthan's%20farming%20community%2C%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Ram%20Singh%20Kaswan%2C%20who%20won%20the%20Churu%20seat%20thrice%20between%201999%20and%202009.%20He%20vows%20to%20split%20the%20Jat%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Modi%20Factor%20And%20The%20Risk%20Of%20Maxing%20Out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20faces%20the%20prospect%20of%20maxing%20out%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20the%20law%20of%20averages%20may%20catch%20up%20with%20the%20party%20this%20year.%20The%20party%20hopes%20that%20the%20Modi%20factor%2C%20which%20is%20very%20strong%20in%20the%20state%2C%20would%20neutralise%20this%20risk.%20In%20the%202019%20national%20elections%2C%20while%20one%20out%20of%20every%20three%20voters%20(32%25)%20on%20an%20average%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20due%20to%20PM%20Modi%2C%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20corresponding%20number%20was%20one%20out%20of%20every%20two%20(49%25).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20Congress%20Script%20A%20Revival%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20hopes%20to%20win%20over%20the%20Gujjar%20community%2C%20which%20overwhelmingly%20supported%20the%20BJP%20in%202019.%20With%20Sachin%20Pilot%20back%20in%20the%20thick%20of%20things%2C%20Gujjar%20votes%20in%20central%20(Jaipur)%20and%20eastern%20Rajasthan%20are%20key%20to%20the%20party's%20revival.%20In%20last%20year's%20state%20polls%2C%2043%25%20of%20Gujjars%20backed%20the%20BJP%2C%20while%2039%25%20supported%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20fought%20well%20in%202023%20and%20saved%20itself%20from%20suffering%20a%20rout.%20Naturally%2C%20it%20hopes%20to%20make%20a%20mark%20this%20time%20around.%20However%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20key%20figures%20like%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20Sachin%20Pilot%20are%20not%20contesting%20the%20elections%20this%20year%20may%20not%20help%20the%20party's%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713348120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F91era2o_pmmodi_640x480_22_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbattle-royale-rajasthan-5-factors-shaping-bjps-hat-trick-bid-5461528%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20latest%20opinion%20polls%20by%20C-Voter%20and%20CNX%20predict%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20sweep%20the%20state%20again%20in%202024%2C%20while%20Polstrat%20gives%2019%20seats%20to%20the%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbattle-royale-rajasthan-5-factors-shaping-bjps-hat-trick-bid-5461528%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Srinath%2C%20umpire%20Menon%20explain%20'Smart%20Replay%20System'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713347859000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109371040%2Cimgsize-42844.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fwatch-match-referee-javagal-srinath-and-umpire-nitin-menon-explain-smart-replay-sy