ra%20and%20Karnataka%20engaged%20in%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20ritual%20was%20carried%20out%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20photos%20of%20him%20watching%20a%20live%20telecast%20of%20the%20event.%20The%20PM%20described%20the%20moment%20as%20%26quot%3Bwonderful%20and%20incomparable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20Nalbari%20meeting%2C%20I%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20witnessing%20the%20wonderful%20and%20incomparable%20moment%20of%20Surya%20Tilak%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20Ayodhya.%20This%20much-awaited%20moment%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20bliss%20for%20everyone.%20This%20Surya%20Tilak%20will%20illuminate%20every%20resolution%20of%20developed%20India%20with%20its%20divine%20energy%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20posted%20on%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAfter%20my%20Nalbari%20rally%2C%20I%20watched%20the%20Surya%20Tilak%20on%20Ram%20Lalla.%20Like%20crores%20of%20Indians%2C%20this%20is%20a%20very%20emotional%20moment%20for%20me.%20The%20grand%20Ram%20Navami%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20historic.%20May%20this%20Surya%20Tilak%20bring%20energy%20to%20our%20lives%20and%20may%20it%20inspire%20our%20nation%20to%20scale%20new%20heights%20of%20glory.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQqDpwOzsTP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FQqDpwOzsTP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1780502125908259263%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20state-of-the-art%20technology%2C%20a%205.8%20centimetre%20ray%20of%20light%20was%20targeted%20onto%20the%20deity's%20forehead.%20This%20feat%20was%20made%20possible%20through%20the%20development%20of%20a%20specialised%20apparatus.%20Ten%20distinguished%20Indian%20scientists%2C%20stationed%20at%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20made%20sure%20that%20the%20ritual%20was%20carried%20out%20smoothly.%20From%20precisely%2012%20noon%2C%20for%20a%20duration%20of%20approximately%203%20to%203.5%20minutes%2C%20sunlight%20was%20channelled%20onto%20the%20statue's%20forehead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20of%20the%20'Surya%20Tilak'%20mechanism%20involved%20collaboration%20between%20scientists%20from%20CBRI%2C%20Roorkee%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Astrophysics%20(IIAP)%2C%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713343980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F6mo4h12o_pm-modi-surya-tilak-_625x300_17_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsurya-tilak-ritual-at-ram-temple-inspired-by-pm-modi-ayodhya-trust-5461147%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20'Surya%20Tilak'%20ceremony%20which%20was%20held%20at%20Ayodhya's%20Ram%20Temple%20today%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Ram%20Navami%20was%20inspired%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20temple's%20construction%20committee's%20chief%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsurya-tilak-ritual-at-ram-temple-inspired-by-pm-modi-ayodhya-trust-5461147%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsurya-tilak-ritual-at-ram-temple-inspired-by-pm-modi-ayodhya-trust-5461147%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsurya-tilak-ritual-at-ram-temple-inspired-by-pm-modi-ayodhya-trust-5461147%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ram%20Lalla's%20forehead%20illuminates%20with%20Surya%20tilak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713343782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109369263%2Cimgsize-536644.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Find